<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<t24help xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
    <header>
        <product>PP</product>
        <title>PPT.PARTYROLE</title>
        <table>PPT.PARTYROLE</table>
    </header>
    <overview>
        <ovdesc>
            <p>This table is used to define different roles of debit and credit parties and map them to relevant tags of a SWIFT payment in the payments hub.</p>
        </ovdesc>
    </overview>
    <menu>
        <t>
            <field>RSCPartyRole</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Record Status Code generated for the record by the payments hub.</p>
                <p>Possible values:</p>
                <p>L - Live</p>
                <p>U - Unapproved</p>
                <p>R - Reversed</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>1 alphanumeric character.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>PartyRole</field>
            <desc>
                <p>The 16 predefined roles can be used to describe the role for Debit/Credit parties.</p>
                <p>INSPTY Instructing Party `50 C or L</p>
                <p>ORDPTY Ordering Party 50 A, F, G, H or K</p>
                <p>SNDINS Sending Institution 51A</p>
                <p>ASVINS Account Servicing Institution 52A or C</p>
                <p>ORDINS Ordering Institution 52A or D</p>
                <p>SNDCBK Sender’s Correspondent Bank 53A, B or D</p>
                <p>RCVCBK Receiver’s Correspondent Bank 54A, B or D</p>
                <p>TRMINS Third Reimbursement Institution 55A, B or D</p>
                <p>SENDER Sender</p>
                <p>IMPDBT Implied Debit Account</p>
                <p>INTINS Intermediary Institution 56 A, C or D</p>
                <p>ACWINS Account with Institution 57 A, B, C or D</p>
                <p>BENINS Beneficiary Institution 58 A or D</p>
                <p>BENFCY Beneficiary 59A or no letter option</p>
                <p>IMPCDT Implied Credit Account</p>
                <p>RECVER Receiver</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>Mandatory Field. 6 alphanumeric characters.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>PartyRoleDescription</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Free Text used to describe the Party Role created.</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>Mandatory Field. 128 alphanumeric characters.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>PartyRoleTag</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Specifies the tag number to be associated with the party role configured</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>Mandatory Field. 6 alphanumeric characters.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>RACPartyRole</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Record Activation Code generated for the record by the payment's hub. </p>
                <p>Possible values:</p>
                <p>N - Not active</p>
                <p>A -  Active</p>
                <p>H - History</p>
                <p>F - Future</p>
                <p>C - Not active future</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>19 alphanumeric characters.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
    </menu>
</t24help>
